T02TD2635E:198b-12: slar yang bkra shis tshigs bcad kyis //
T02TD2635E:198b-13: dus gsum du ni khrus bya'o //
T02TD2635E:198b-14: de nas me tog spos la sogs //
T02TD2635E:198b-15: thams cad kyang ni dbul bar bya //
T02TD2635E:198b-16: lam sbyangs pa yi sngags kyis ni //
T02TD2635E:198b-17: me tog char ni dbab par bya //
T02TD2635E:198b-18: de ltar zhag ni gnyis gsum nas //
T02TD2635E:198b-19: zhag brgyad pa yi bar du bya //
T02TD2635E:198b-20: sa bzung nyi ma nas brtsams te /
T02TD2635E:198b-21: slob ma gzhug pa'i bar du bya //
T02TD2635E:198b-22: rab tu gnas pa'i dus su ni //
T02TD2635E:198b-23: bum pa la sogs gshegs su gsol //
T02TD2635E:198b-24: de nas de yi cha ru ni //
T02TD2635E:198b-25: sngar bshad pa yi rim pa ni //
T02TD2635E:198b-26: padma dkar po la gnas pa'i //
T02TD2635E:198b-27: 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad mdzes par bri //
T02TD2635E:198b-28: de la slob ma bzhag nas ni //
T02TD2635E:198b-29: bum pa bzang po dkar bcas pas //
T02TD2635E:198b-30: sngar bshad cho ga bzhin du ni //
T02TD2635E:198b-31: 'bad de dbang bskur sbyin par bya //
T02TD2635E:198b-32: de nas yid la ci 'dod kun //
T02TD2635E:198b-33: phongs pa med par dbul bar bya //
T02TD2635E:198b-34: gtan pa med pa'i mchod sbyin gyis //
T02TD2635E:198b-35: kun la rnam par sbyin par bya //
T02TD2635E:198b-36: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal gyis bcings pa'i //
T02TD2635E:198b-37: 'gro ba rigs drug la gnas pa'i //
T02TD2635E:198b-38: dkyil 'khor du ni bkrus tsam gyis //
T02TD2635E:198b-39: sdug bsngal kun las grol bar 'gyur //
T02TD2635E:198b-40: 'jug pa dang ni mthong ba yi //
T02TD2635E:198b-41: de yi bsod nams tshad med pas //
T02TD2635E:198b-42: dmyal ba yi dags byol song gi /'gro ba kun las de zlog nas //
T02TD2635E:198b-43: sum cu rtsa gsum yang na ni //
T02TD2635E:198b-44: dga' ldan gnas su yang dag skye //
T02TD2635E:198b-45: lho phyogs kyi sgor bya ba'i cho ga'o /
T02TD2635E:198b-47: // / de nas sngon bzhin dkyil 'khor la //
T02TD2635E:198b-48: mchod pa byas nas rdzogs par bya //
T02TD2635E:198b-49: rang gi bskyed pa snying gar bsdu //
T02TD2635E:198b-50: spyan drangs lha ni gshegs su gsol //
T02TD2635E:198b-51: aom khyed kyis sems can don kun mdzod //
T02TD2635E:199a-0: sangs rgyas yul du gshegs nas @199a * //
T02TD2635E:199a-2: / slar yang sems can don la gshegs //
T02TD2635E:199a-3: zhes brjod se gol lan gsum brdeg / aa k'a ro mu kham sarba dharm'a n'am a'adya nutpanna tv'a da mu:/
T02TD2635E:199a-4: zhes bya bas dkyil 'khor bsdus nas su //
T02TD2635E:199a-5: sa tshon chu bo chen por bskyal //
T02TD2635E:199a-6: zhal bsro khung bu dgang ba dang //
T02TD2635E:199a-7: sbyin sreg 'khor lo nor gang yod //
T02TD2635E:199a-8: de kun slob dpon kho na'i dbang //
T02TD2635E:199a-9: de ltar rdo rje 'dzin pas gsungs //
T02TD2635E:199a-11: ba yi lci bas byugs byas te //
T02TD2635E:199a-12: rdul tshon dkar po gcig pu yis //
T02TD2635E:199a-14: shes rab pha rol phyin ston te //
T02TD2635E:199a-15: sa bdag slob ma phyogs skyong rnams //
T02TD2635E:199a-16: zhi bar bya ba'i don du yang //
T02TD2635E:199a-17: gong du gsungs pa'i sreg rdzas kyis //
T02TD2635E:199a-18: slob ma'i lag tu bzung nas su //
T02TD2635E:199a-19: zhi ba'i sbyin sreg bya ba'o //
T02TD2635E:199a-20: sems can don sogs bya ba la //
T02TD2635E:199a-21: grogs por gyur phyir lha rnams la //
T02TD2635E:199a-22: gsol ba btab nas dge rtsa ni //
T02TD2635E:199a-23: yongs su bsngos nas rdzogs par bya //
T02TD2635E:199a-24: dpal ldan ngan song sbyong ba yi //
T02TD2635E:199a-25: cho ga sh'akya mgon gyis gsungs //
T02TD2635E:199a-26: dkyil 'khor cho ga ma lus pa //
T02TD2635E:199a-27: yongs su nyams par gyur par mthong //
T02TD2635E:199a-28: bla ma rdo rje can drin gyis //
T02TD2635E:199a-29: dkyil 'khor cho ga sbyar ba las//
T02TD2635E:199a-30: bdag gis bsod nams gang thob pa //
T02TD2635E:199a-31: des ni sems can ma lus kun //
T02TD2635E:199a-32: kun mkhyen ye shes mnga' brnyes nas //
T02TD2635E:199a-33: sangs rgyas dang ni 'dra bar shog / ngan song thams cad yongs su sbyong ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga slob dpon kun dga' snying bos mdzad pa rdzogs so /
